metadata.name: Hide Your Bags - Whale Bag
metadata.description: Hide Your Bags (HYB) is a collection of 8,888 digital game cards living on the Ethereum blockchain as 12 unique ERC-1155 tokens. MINTING HYB gets you the IRL card game for free. Minting OR holding HYB at the time of our GameMaster snapshot will earn you the opportunity to claim a GameMaster PFP for free (20 ETH of digital card value = 1 GameMaster PFP). As a team we are committed to bringing insane IRL and web3 utility to the community. Visit goodmorning-games.com for more information.
